      "raw_text": "Williams, as expressed in the COM\nployers.\n\n\nAS yet there has been no action\ntaken by the contracting painters and\nbuilders, and not a word will be said\nas to what the action is likely to be\nwhen the matter is finally taken up.\n\n\nBY some of the representatives, of\nthe trades council, and others who\nare interested in the labor question,\nit was thought to be wise idea if\nthe council would accept the five men\nproposed by the painting and building\ncontractors, and name five others, and\nlet these 10 men choose the eleventh.\nmaking the beard eleven instead of\nseven. as at first proposed."
